            <abstract id="ref3" label="Abstract">The 
                <emph render="italic">New York Review</emph> Archive is a small collection of correspondence to the 
                <emph render="italic">New York Review</emph>'s editor, Peter McCurtin. McCurtin edited the 
                <emph render="italic">New York Review</emph> with William Atkins in 1958.</abstract>
